1 SECTION 3. TRANSFER - BIOSCIENCE INNOVATION GRANT FUND TO LIFE SCIENCE
2 DEVELOPMENT FUND. The office of management and budget shall transfer any balance in
3 the bioscience innovation grant fund to the life science development fund on June 30, 2025.
4 SECTION 4. APPROPRIATION - TRANSFER TO LIFE SCIENCE DEVELOPMENT FUND.
5 There is appropriated out of any moneys in the general fund in the state treasury, not otherwise
6 appropriated, the sum of $12,000,000, which the office of management and budget shall
7 transfer to the life science development fund, for the period beginning with the effective date of
8 this Act, and ending June 30, 2027.
9 SECTION 5. EMERGENCY. Sections 1, 3, and 4 of this Act are declared to be an
10 emergency measure.
